  Atari tracker formats:

  CDx1	****+	Octalyser		CD61, CD81
  DTM	***	Digital Tracker		1.9
  FA0x	****+	Digital Tracker		FA04, FA06, FA08
  FLX	****	Flextrax		M.K., xCHN (no dsp effects)
  GTK	**	Graoumf Tracker		GTK1, GTK4
